dct_description_sm: Gazetteer on verso. Includes glossary. Shows the territory acquired from and given to the GDR in the 1988 exchange. Berlin boundary, Berlin East-West boundary, sector and district boundaries, traffic control 20 mile zone radius. Includes an index to streets, subways stations, parks, rivers, lakes, canals and places. "801356 (544417) 6-89."
